--- !u!114 &255359445
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 255359444}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 595f36b8364a0d84dbc23835822c0f8e, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LoreController
  displayImage: {fileID: 89902178}
  displayText: {fileID: 929303874}
  fadeImage: {fileID: 277666948}
  continuePromptText: {fileID: 0}
  slides:
  - slideImage: {fileID: -8995907195012914875, guid: 500dc320a932747f1aa8319b6c025b3a, type: 3}
    slideText: 'Far, far away, there was a kingdom full of bacterias. One day, a
      new specie appeared nearby them: "The Jellies".'
  - slideImage: {fileID: -1243543691578603617, guid: 90295607256c0452e8d5e45be3332108, type: 3}
    slideText: They were meant to stay in peace, but a mysterious figure, known as
      "THE TONE WHO RULES" decided to reject them. Putting them away as "food for
      other better bacterias"
  - slideImage: {fileID: -7774470285513859302, guid: 159a4dc15a3324f568e2562c4ec17ccd, type: 3}
    slideText: THE ONE WHO RULES possessed the ARCHEOTYPE, a source of infinite power.
      The machine had the power of the legendary king ARCHEA.
  - slideImage: {fileID: -5358246196399628597, guid: 8d1de3219507741e492abc83714ba5d4, type: 3}
    slideText: But you, you are the one who will take us to MONERA again. Gain the
      energy and the power from the ones that want us away and kill THE ONE WHO RULES
  - slideImage: {fileID: -7774470285513859302, guid: 159a4dc15a3324f568e2562c4ec17ccd, type: 3}
    slideText: Take us home again, son. we need you, MONERA needs you.
  revealCharsPerSecond: 24
  fadeDuration: 0.5
  finalFadeOutDuration: 2
  nextSceneIntroFadeDuration: 3
  nextSceneIntroFadeSteps: 24
  nextSceneIndex: 2
  continuePromptFontSize: 22
  continuePromptColor: {r: 0.7, g: 0.7, b: 0.7, a: 0.92}
  continuePromptScreenOffset: {x: -40, y: 28}
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 353ce1c21094e45e9bcdf8e707a1b8b9, type: 3}
  typingVolume: 0.6
  minTimeBetweenSounds: 0.02
